  "id": "api/platform-server/renderApplication",
  "title": "renderApplication",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-server\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-server\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-server/renderApplication\", \"name\": \"renderApplication\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/platform-server\">@angular/platform-server</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/platform-server/src/utils.ts?message=docs(platform-server)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L115-L192\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/14.1.0-next.0/packages/platform-server/src/utils.ts#L115-L192\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"renderapplication\">renderApplication<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server/renderApplication#renderapplication\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"This API is in Developer Preview\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">developer preview</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">引导 Angular 应用程序的实例并将其呈现为字符串。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Bootstraps an instance of an Angular application and renders it to a string.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/renderApplication#description\">查看\"说明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/renderApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">renderApplication</a></span>&#x3C;T>(rootComponent: <a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type</a>&#x3C;T>, options: { appId: string; document?: string; url?: string; providers?: (<a href=\"api/core/Provider\" class=\"code-anchor\">Provider</a> | <a href=\"api/core/ImportedNgModuleProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">ImportedNgModuleProviders</a>)[]; platformProviders?: <a href=\"api/core/Provider\" class=\"code-anchor\">Provider</a>[]; }): Promise&#x3C;string></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>rootComponent</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/core/Type\" class=\"code-anchor\">Type&#x3C;T></a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">对应该呈现的独立组件的引用。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A reference to a Standalone Component that should be rendered.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>options</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>object</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">渲染操作的附加配置：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Additional configuration for the render operation:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">  <code>appId</code> - 此应用程序的字符串标识符。 appId 用于在 TransferState\n用例中作为应用程序的所有服务器生成的样式和状态键的前缀。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>appId</code> - a string identifier of this application. The appId is used to prefix all\nserver-generated stylings and state keys of the application in TransferState\nuse-cases.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>document</code> - 要呈现的页面的完整文档 HTML，以字符串形式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>document</code> - the full document HTML of the page to render, as a string.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>url</code> - 当前呈现请求的 URL。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>url</code> - the URL for the current render request.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>providers</code> - 当前渲染请求的应用程序级提供程序集。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>providers</code> - set of application level providers for the current render request.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>platformProviders</code> - 当前渲染请求的平台级提供程序。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>platformProviders</code> - the platform level providers for the current render request.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">一个 Promise，一旦解析，就会返回序列化（到字符串）呈现的页面。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>Promise&#x3C;string></code>: A Promise, that returns serialized (to a string) rendered page, once resolved.</p>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server/renderApplication#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">注意：传递给此函数的根组件<em>必须</em>是独立的（应该在 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> 装饰器配置中具有 <code>standalone: true</code>\n标志）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Note: the root component passed into this function <em>must</em> be a standalone one (should have the\n<code>standalone: true</code> flag in the <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> decorator config).</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a> ({\n  standalone: true,\n  template: 'Hello world!'\n})\nclass RootComponent {}\n\nconst output: string = await <a href=\"api/platform-server/renderApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">renderApplication</a>(RootComponent, {appId: 'server-app'});\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-server\n - api/platform-server/BEFORE_APP_SERIALIZED\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/ImportedNgModuleProviders\n - api/core/Provider\n - api/core/Type\n - api/platform-server\n - api/platform-server/renderApplication#description\n - api/platform-server/renderApplication#renderapplication\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/platform-server/src/utils.ts?message=docs(platform-server)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L115-L192\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/14.1.0-next.0/packages/platform-server/src/utils.ts#L115-L192\n-->"
}